review_data: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2019
name: crazyartdolls
title: Excellent product life saver.
review: I am in the middle of chemo treatment and this product help me so much.I am a. Vegan so I have to watch what I eat otherwise I get nauseated.I have one of these in the morning and night before bed to keep my blood sugar up. I wake up feeling good, would recommend for anyone even if you are not sick.Also, found out I can use my amazon card to pay for it.

title: Ewww
review: I was expecting a chocolate pudding kind of taste, it's sour and very weird tasting. Not edible. Won't order this flavor again, but I do like most all of their other flavors and eat this brand of yogurt nearly every day!

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on April 13, 2021
name: Jen
title: Omg!? ‘So Delicious’ is an understatement
review: I have never felt compelled to review a grocery item until now. This is THE best yogurt alternative I’ve ever tried; I wish I had bought a whole case! So creamy, not chalky like dairy yogurt, just overall a delicious product, must try!

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on March 25, 2021
name: WLC
title: Very good, hard to find this flavor
review: I like this yogurt a lot!! I cannot have milk or nuts.... I love chocolate and it is very very hard to find this, or any, non-dairy, nut-free CHOCOLATE yogurt. If you shake it up good before opening, it is smooth and flavorful. I love the vanilla too. Good non-dairy yogurt!

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on March 14, 2021
name: Saleem Rana
title: A chocolate dream
review: Just the right amount of chocolate in the perfect plant-based yogurt. Glad they make them in small tubs. I would probably polish off a pound-sized tub in ten minutes. Always out of stock. The company should triple production!

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on February 23, 2021

title: Would not buy again
review: I really like this brand and I love their yogurts, but unfortunately, this flavor is not my favorite. It tasted kind of strange the flavor. Other than that their other flavors are amazing but I would not buy this flavor again.

review: This yogurt is delicious.I give it to my 4 year old and he loves it.It is not like having yogurt, more like a dessert.
